{"tid":12324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【捐款啦望】美國學者睇唔過眼眾籌出粵英詞典","createTime":"2016-11-29T15:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T06:05:09.000Z","uid":12185,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff11fccc1d1faeaaff43266559be115f400cd9e7","tid":12324,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:09:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">捐款link: <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/wenlin/wenlin-abc-cantonese-dictionary-website-ed-robert\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fwenlin%2Fwenlin-abc-cantonese-dictionary-website-ed-robert&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=eb219e9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/wenlin/wenlin-abc-cantonese-dictionary-website-ed-robert</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n美國一位教授聯同「文林研究所」在外國眾籌網頁搞眾籌，希望製作網上和實體版粵英詞典，出心出力保育廣東話文化，你又會否支持？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>對上一本相對全面的廣東話詞典，是於1977年由香港 (英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）政府編印的</strong>，今次就由一位美國學者包睿舜主理。包睿舜是美國人，在1972年起開始研究漢語，醉心研究粵語逾40年。他曾在理工大學及香港大學任教語言學，出版了數本粵語書籍，他更可教香港人粵語正音。他曾表示粵語對香港非常重要，<strong>「你或會以為近年應有人出版字典，但對上一本較為全面的粵英詞典其實是在1977年出版！」</strong>包睿舜更直言在香港要找到一本好的詞典實在有難度，<strong>「因為在詞典中，根本找不到現在流行的粵語口語，這令人十分難過。」</strong><br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20161127/19846701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20161127%2F19846701&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=04f2f948\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20161127%2F19846701&h=df22f5f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20161127/19846701</a><br />\n請大家幫手share出去同埋捐吓款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼佬越黎越少途徑接觸廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499ae3969cb7bad96211c5f6d2cd4a8cb9015bd4","tid":12324,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"33b2d6258da0d6c44ea7a94122fa8a2833e5b0fb","tid":12324,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"連本字典都冇，你點樣教人講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係英國<br />\n有兩個鬼佬一見到我就同我講流利普通話<br />\n但冇人識講廣東話<br />\n面家人地個語言強過我地啦<br />\n一定要反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d427f9648448edf792d9dab594a1e629b70b4fc6","tid":12324,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d863a6a7fa80dfda21d70bb099f088617d73a08b","tid":12324,"uid":9082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c3af5f150c59c974aa48e57e43d9ec688d75b24","tid":12324,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"唔係淨係捐款架，<br />\n捐完之後如果個project成到事<br />\n佢會回禮番俾你<br />\n你捐果陣可以揀要咩回禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而如果成唔到事就唔會扣你錢"},{"pid":"be66e391e0eaabc18e196e7a5c78ee189bc351eb","tid":12324,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已捐。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380be5ea9a4ef92632ef6c7e19d27df9c375134f","tid":12324,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:16:55.000Z","msg":"何文匯條撚屌D fd?"},{"pid":"e1b11f016e8c6757d9a3384b2fdaa808aed12642","tid":12324,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29